    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable partner on the road. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so you can count on it for many more miles. It's clean, runs great, and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next adventure! If you're looking for a dependable ride that's ready to go, this is the one for you. Drop me a message if you'd like to come see it!",
