    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46-generation M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. Mechanical integrity has been prioritized, with a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to maintain structural rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings, providing the telepathic turn-in these chassis are known for. While the Alpine White finish shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery and a crisp exhaust note. A mechanically sound specimen ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
