    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior features a deep metallic finish that catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, superficial road wear expected of a well-loved car. Inside, you\u2019ll find a spacious, smoke-free cabin with premium upholstery that remains supple and supportive. All electronics, from the intuitive infotainment system to the crisp dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in great health; it boasts a complete service history, including a recent preventative maintenance check and a fresh set of all-season tires. It drives smooth and quiet, offering a responsive handling experience that makes every commute a pleasure. This is a dependable, well-cared-for example ready for its next owner to drive away with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
