      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty car, and I think you're going to love it! It's in really wonderful shape and has been so reliable for me. It's super clean, runs beautifully, and is just waiting for someone new to take it on its next adventure. If you're looking for a solid, well-loved vehicle that's ready to hit the road today, this is definitely the one. Drop me a message if you'd like to come take a look!",
