    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity, including a complete VANOS system refresh and proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein B6 dampers and Powerflex bushings for sharpened turn-in response without sacrificing streetability. While the aesthetic reflects a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the drivetrain is dialed in, featuring a valve adjustment and rod bearing service completed within the last 15k miles. A mechanically sound example ready for the B-roads.",
